messages.text:
The no digging garden allows people cultivate food in containers which has a lot more benefits;

conserve water, prevent erosion, and control weeds and pests more easily.

This is in contrast with traditional agriculture where cultivation happens in open ground. In case the crops and soil are more susceptible to the changing environment.

